  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      improve detection and management of suicide risk among depressed patients in primary care
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      After intervention of training on the identification and management of depression and suicide
      risk in primary health care professionals, the ability of detection and management of suicide
      risk among depressed patients in primary care is expected to be improved compared to baseline
      evaluation.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
